MISSION:IMPOSSIBLE  The 1988 TV SEASON  4 Episodes 

Episodes: 

#1- The Killer 
When Jim Phelp's protege is murdered,he comes out of retirement to catch the killer and organize a new team of IMF agent's. 

#2- The System 
To shut down a major crime syndicate, the team tries to turn a high profile mobster against his boss. 

#3- Holagrams 
The team must try to extradite an international drug lord who's running a world wide trafficking ring. 

#4- The Condemned 
The team works to free a former IMF agent who was falsely imprisoned for murder, and now faces execution. This mission hit's close to home, as the agent is Jim's ex-colleague and Grant's father, Barney Collier.
